'''國家儲蓄及投資銀行'''（{{lang-en|National Savings and Investments|National Savings and Investments, NS&I}}，前稱：'''郵政儲蓄銀行'''及'''國家儲蓄銀行'''）是英國一家儲蓄[[銀行|銀行]]，亦為[[英國政府|英國政府]][[英國財政部|財政部]]部門之一<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ns-i |title=NS&I |publisher=GOV.UK |accessdate=14 February 2014 |archive-date=2020-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230153504/https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ns-i |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://nsandi-corporate.com/about-nsi/who-we-are |title=Who we are NS&I Corporate Site |publisher=Nsandi.com |date=9 September 2015 |accessdate=2021-01-09 |archive-date=2018-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180606215006/http://nsandi-corporate.com/about-nsi/who-we-are/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。 該銀行提供免稅並獲英國政府全額保障的存款產品，並為[[英國政府|英國政府]]提供9%的財政[[赤字|赤字]]支援。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ig.com/uk/investments/news/investing/2018/07/30/doomed-if-interest-rates-go-up--the-uk-government-already-spends|title=Doomed if interest rates go up? The UK government already spends £49 billion on debt interest|last=Smith|first=Oliver|date=30 July 2018|website=IG Markets|language=en-gb|access-date=2020-02-24|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111130303/https://www.ig.com/uk/investments/news/investing/2018/07/30/doomed-if-interest-rates-go-up--the-uk-government-already-spends|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

==產品及服務==
該银行提供儲蓄戶口、投资戶口、收息债券、彩票债券（Premium Bonds）等<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thisismoney.co.uk/money/saving/article-8755259/NS-make-savage-cuts-rates-Premium-Bonds-November.html |title=NS&I savings bloodbath: Premium Bonds odds to lengthen hugely while one easy-access rate will drop to just 0.01% after 'savage' cuts |publisher=This is Money |accessdate=21 September 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104192025/https://www.thisismoney.co.uk/money/saving/article-8755259/NS-make-savage-cuts-rates-Premium-Bonds-November.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2020年底，該银行總存款為316億英磅<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thisismoney.co.uk/money/saving/article-9111337/Savers-withdrew-staggering-6-2bn-NS-accounts-November.html |title=Savers withdrew a staggering £6.2bn from NS&I accounts in November after rate cuts... as January's Premium Bonds winners are named |publisher=This is Money |accessdate=4 January 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106075910/https://www.thisismoney.co.uk/money/saving/article-9111337/Savers-withdrew-staggering-6-2bn-NS-accounts-November.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

